==English==
===Verb===
'''[[give]] [[in]]'''
#to [[collapse]] or [[fall]]
#:''The roof '''gave in''' under the weight of the snow.''
#to [[relent]] or [[yield]]
#:''I finally '''gave in''' and let him stay up to watch TV.''

